0 & 0  &  2  & 2  \\  \hline
$2$ & 0  &  $2/(1)$  &   $2$  \\ \hline
& 1  &  1  & (2)   \\ \hline
$4$ & 0 &  1 & 2 \\ \hline
 & 1 &  1 & (2)   \\ \hline
